Hello dear cyborg, human, or otherwise beautiful being.
This is the start-here page of the infrastructure side of ipfs.io.

It is especially meant for:

- the IPFS infrastructure team who operate ipfs.io
- anyone interested in a living IPFS case study

Private services:

- private networking using cjdns
- metrics.ipfs.team
- archives access
- infrastructure deployment

Public services:

- IPFS' default bootstrap nodes
- a public IPFS gateway
- website hosting through IPNS+DNS
- the ipfs project website
- storage of archive mirrors
- dist.ipfs.io, ipfs distributions download
- status.ipfs.io, public metrics dashboard
- cjdns connectivity for gateway and bootstrappers
- cjdns public peers

Tools that have emerged from IPFS operations:

- Provsn
- HSHCA by Neocities
- multireq
- go-dnslink


